{"tid":1735073,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"開路去理大 雙重圍魏之法","createTime":"2019-11-18T13:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:25.000Z","uid":76600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5195cf549b33dcd8820717afcba7216c2c864d3","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"而家彌敦道手足既問題係 開唔到路去理大。<br />\n如果我地開唔到路，咁不如要佢地自己比條路出黎。<br />\n叫尖沙咀手足燒狗屋 封晒尖沙咀狗屋出入口。<br />\n入面班狗出唔到黎 一定會叫最近既油麻地 佐敦黎增援。<br />\n咁原本守路既個班狗就自動走左，可以由彌敦道轉入理大。"},{"pid":"0b38932a9b97e983fef233a5255306045318d088","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"推 現場有冇其他人睇到"},{"pid":"2b9868ef95e0a251d5710c2a689d615836741acc","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"後面on99企晒係到"},{"pid":"46a92b17191dcb13e04c26ea1e8985399381e2f0","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"手足睇到嗎"},{"pid":"65495cfecd742d1e829064bb1b187f5a2a8d0809","tid":1735073,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100cd074f9ee9588893b302e133ec4ee2d3c4f7c","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀手足"},{"pid":"ed29c6e835f9451b6cd2eaecf91d622ddb7f3310","tid":1735073,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳予身處理大人士】<br />\n<br />\n不少消息指，今晚或會有社會賢達或政府社工獲批准進入理大，陪同或勸籲抗爭者和平離開（但很可能會被捕）。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯呼籲，無論你離開的方式如何，在任何情況下，請勿向任何人表達你「投降」或「自首」，因這樣有可能影響你日後的法律權利，緊記！"},{"pid":"8ee5dd0c5341b5a4dda15c31a5c4ff4b37334315","tid":1735073,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"投你老母 一條警犬都未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95955157d1799340d8939ace178a8a51aa71cf2e","tid":1735073,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:14:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9e54971048cdf2ec32f8c775cf06233921e8ab0","tid":1735073,"uid":76600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"同埋油麻地 佐敦 旺角手足 唔好走 前線打緊架"},{"pid":"8d72e06a5f40052c8bcf88123f043ed30b4f2e0c","tid":1735073,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08aa3333e0d247812741a53cbc268113ab9ec4d","tid":1735073,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"快D成堆人衝去啦仲留係度不停食TG"},{"pid":"b8415ab4ea83b6bdcffdd77a3476d366c4d1952b","tid":1735073,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"如果有車開路"}]}